OL,4,Ccryptosporidium outbreak at farm
OL,5,Creaches 81
OL,7,FThe number of people who have
OL,8,Fcontracted a parasitic infection
OL,9,Flinked to animal feeding sessions at a
OL,10,Ffarm in south Wales has now reached 81.
OL,12,FSeven new cases of cryptosporidium
OL,13,Fhave been confirmed since last week,
OL,14,Fall linked to visits to Cowbridge Farm
OL,15,FShop, Marlborough Grange Farm in the
OL,16,FVale of Glamorgan, during March and
OL,17,FApril.
OL,19,FThe infection has led to 16 people
OL,20,Frequiring hospital care for at least
OL,21,Fone night.
