OL,7,FOfficials from Public Health Wales
OL,8,F(PHW) and other agencies met on
OL,9,FWednesday for the fourth time since
OL,10,Fthe outbreak began to co-ordinate the
OL,11,Fresponse.
OL,13,FThe farm stopped all public feeding
OL,14,Fsessions involving animals, including
OL,15,Fcalves and lambs, on April 29 and
OL,16,Fcontinues to co-operate with the
OL,17,Finvestigation.
