OL,7,FSymptoms of cryptospridium, which is
OL,8,Fcommonly associated with farm animals,
OL,9,Ftypically appear two to 10 days after
OL,10,Fexposure and can last up to two weeks.
OL,12,FPHW warned that infection can still
OL,13,Fspread after symptoms subside and has
OL,14,Furged those affected not to go
OL,15,Fswimming for two weeks.
