OL,7,FVisitors to petting farms are being
OL,8,Freminded to avoid close contact with
OL,9,Fanimals, supervise children closely,
OL,10,Fand wash hands thoroughly with soap
OL,11,Fand warm water after touching animals
OL,12,For walking around a farm.
OL,14,FAlcohol hand gels do not provide
OL,15,Fsufficient protection. Pregnant women
OL,16,Fare also being advised to steer clear
OL,17,Fof newborn lambs during lambing season
OL,18,Fdue to a higher risk of infection.
